forbidden.name: shared-cannot-depend-on-other-layers
forbidden.comment: A camada 'shared'  a base e no pode depender de nenhuma outra camada superior.

forbidden.name: entities-cannot-depend-on-higher-layers
forbidden.comment: Entidades devem ser autocontidas e no podem depender de features, widgets, pages ou app.

forbidden.name: features-cannot-depend-on-higher-layers
forbidden.comment: Features no podem depender de widgets, pages ou app.

forbidden.name: widgets-cannot-depend-on-higher-layers
forbidden.comment: Widgets no podem depender de pages ou app.

forbidden.name: pages-cannot-depend-on-app
forbidden.comment: Pages no podem depender da camada app.

forbidden.name: no-circular
forbidden.comment: Dependncias circulares so proibidas pois tornam o cdigo frgil e imprevisvel.

forbidden.name: no-orphans
forbidden.comment: Mdulos rfos (no utilizados) devem ser removidos para manter a base de cdigo limpa.

forbidden.name: not-to-dev-dep
forbidden.comment: No importe pacotes de desenvolvimento (devDependencies) no cdigo fonte da aplicao (src).

forbidden.name: no-deprecated
forbidden.comment: Evite usar dependncias marcadas como deprecadas.

forbidden.name: not-to-spec
forbidden.comment: O cdigo fonte no deve importar mdulos de teste.
